{"tid":1150601,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"母親節,整荼樓點心比老母食，點知比佢罵我小家","createTime":"2019-05-12T03:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T08:01:25.000Z","uid":40226,"like":48,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d78c3ca99580e17c74253bee2f9e0c62a485e9b5","tid":1150601,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T03:33:09.000Z","msg":"年年老母節 老母都會神咁早7點就叫全家去飲荼<br />\n仲要次次屈9我比錢 +專登叫埋哂d特點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當正自己係老母就大哂咁 兒童節又唔見兒童大哂?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我岩岩考完DSE 日日都同D fd子出街玩<br />\n又未搵到署期工 邊有咁多閒錢請老母飲荼呀<br />\n3條友加埋 起碼都要200蚊埋單啦<br />\n仲要老母節收得特別貴tim D荼樓正一仆街黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我就諗到條屎橋 親手下廚扮孝順 又可以慳返d錢<br />\n結果6點半起身就開始整啦<br />\n<br />\n食材如下:<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.amoy.com/images/cms/product/00000000305.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amoy.com%2Fimages%2Fcms%2Fproduct%2F00000000305.jpg&h=b38d36be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.amoy.com/images/cms/product/00000000059.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amoy.com%2Fimages%2Fcms%2Fproduct%2F00000000059.jpg&h=5b684ab9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蝦餃燒賣呢d就基本啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/shrimpsalad81/1211563431.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fshrimpsalad81%2F1211563431.jpg&h=6e2c4637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/shrimpsalad81/1211563431.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fshrimpsalad81%2F1211563431.jpg&h=6e2c4637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.amoy.com/images/cms/product/00000000078.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amoy.com%2Fimages%2Fcms%2Fproduct%2F00000000078.jpg&h=b93462a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n包類就易塞飽老母個肚 所以整三包<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.daihung.com/photos/DSC02365.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.daihung.com%2Fphotos%2FDSC02365.jpg&h=030f7b00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n珍珠雞就貴野黎既 平時飲荼好少叫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/640pix/20040314/Article_LiveMag/14mb45p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20040314%2FArticle_LiveMag%2F14mb45p.jpg&h=f276738d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老母平時鐘意食粥 所以特意買多碗皮強獸肉粥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ccue.com/tor/hotdeals/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/20110329-093217.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ccue.com%2Ftor%2Fhotdeals%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2011%2F03%2F20110329-093217.jpg&h=729e7652&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ccue.com/tor/hotdeals/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/20110329-093217.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ccue.com%2Ftor%2Fhotdeals%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2011%2F03%2F20110329-093217.jpg&h=729e7652&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麵就我自己食既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  鐘意食點心的人都on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img10.360buyimg.com/n1/jfs/t16780/148/1530749380/139851/e51bf997/5acc6c0fNd0949837.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg10.360buyimg.com%2Fn1%2Fjfs%2Ft16780%2F148%2F1530749380%2F139851%2Fe51bf997%2F5acc6c0fNd0949837.jpg&h=1f9f96af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後再沖埋香片 咁先match返去荼樓飲茶果種感覺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我就滿心歡喜 叫老母起身飲荼<br />\n點知老母一見到D點心就話我小家 串我請一餐荼都唔肯<br />\n我咪同佢嘈 :依家咪請你飲荼囉 有乜分別呀 點解你咁貪慕虛榮一定要食大荼樓~<br />\n<br />\n都唔知係咪佢陳晚打麻雀輸錢 搵我黎出氣<br />\n猛咁話生叉燒好過生我 仲拎d叉燒包掉我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我慶慶地(D包好撚熱) 拎返D燒賣掉佢還擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢即刻話以後唔比零用錢我 之後沖左落街 (我估佢9成係去同D雀友飲荼+打麻雀)<br />\n<br />\n結果得返老豆同埋我 食哂D點心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n谷鳩撚氣 天日仲約左fd子唱通k d錢用左黎買點心 依家都唔知點算..."},{"pid":"bbbff70488fa79a258e168f9c577eed539ca68b9","tid":1150601,"uid":186844,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T03:35:22.000Z","msg":"1/10 字數分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515b1282fa1724dfbc3aa1ab70ccfbd5e13c38ee","tid":1150601,"uid":75712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T03:36:02.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"4d01877b0297495d8a1eba007e2de7267732636a","tid":1150601,"uid":41366,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"又撚新會然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw祝大家母親節快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a479c18a860297b49d7e717dc58078873c3f65","tid":1150601,"uid":229767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T03:46:16.000Z","msg":"都唔係親手整，不如去飲茶"},{"pid":"e858adcf4f921479ff6450c806f3ed52c1ce6786","tid":1150601,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T03:47:49.000Z","msg":"又嚟"},{"pid":"2030e6312caaf31e67aab7b4ea90e9f6201a1cb2","tid":1150601,"uid":4206,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T03:55:15.000Z","msg":"今晚應該會有埋倒湯潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96df8ceaf3e199dba51fdf301bfdcbec95d654f","tid":1150601,"uid":10604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T04:12:48.000Z","msg":"睇一次笑一次"},{"pid":"4a53c37eee4a28b5b017402fd5979695545451ed","tid":1150601,"uid":128164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T05:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\